{"tid":282850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世界盃亞洲區十二強賽　內戰敘利亞對支那 2:2打和","createTime":"2017-06-13T16:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T17:11:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05897f83594ab6dabf29c414c95b1f80b7cf7529","tid":282850,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1335964-20170613.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1335964-20170613.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2F3W59dA5bVXR%2FQ5nWn%2BkBW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4105a7bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1335964-20170613.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7340d86e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1335964-20170613.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">世界盃亞洲區十二強賽　敘利亞和支那 2:2</span></strong><br />\n2017-06-13 HKT 23:52<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界盃亞洲區十二強賽，敘利亞2:2 和支那。支那在上半場12分鐘失守，換邊後，支那憑郜林及吳曦先後建功，反先2:1。補時3分鐘，敘利亞憑薩利赫的自由球破門，追平2:2完場。<br />\n<br />\n支那目前8戰1勝3和，6分暫列第五，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出線機會非常渺茫</span></span>。支那隊下場將會主場迎戰烏茲別克。"},{"pid":"d0b6e72dfc765857c7e0eb7cf4dfcab88227d8c5","tid":282850,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T17:10:44.000Z","msg":"8場6分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be032d4053f1b4d93cbd852f6adb652d5f431cc3","tid":282850,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}